subdefinitions.definition: Of or associated with the city of Kyiv (the capital city of Ukraine ).

definitions.definition: Of or associated with the city of Kiev , especially when referring to the medieval period (c. 880–c. 1150) when the city dominated the East Slavic lands which today are Belarus , Russia , and Ukraine .

secondary_definitions: ( historical ) Of or associated with the city of Kiev , especially when referring to the medieval period (c. 880–c. 1150) when the city dominated the East Slavic lands which today are Belarus , Russia , and Ukraine .
